---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Education & Training Services | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Professional technology education and training services including software development, AI, cybersecurity, and cloud computing training in the UAE."
  path="/services/education-training/"
>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <img width="48" src="/img/logo.webp" alt="GeneralSoft Logo"/>
        <span class="logo-text">Generalsoft<span class="logo-legal">FZ-LLC</span></span>
      </a>
      <span class="lang-switch"><a href="/ar/services/education-training/">العربية</a></span>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li class="dropdown">
          <a href="#services" class="dropbtn">Services <span class="dropdown-arrow">▼</span></a>
          <div class="dropdown-content">
            <a href="/services/custom-software/">Custom Software Development</a>
            <a href="/services/education-training/">Education & Training</a>
            <a href="/services/ai-development/">AI Development</a>
            <a href="/services/systems-design/">Systems & Software Design</a>
            <a href="/services/cyber-security/">Cyber Security</a>
            <a href="/services/web-design/">Web & Network Design</a>
            <a href="/services/mobile-apps/">Mobile Applications</a>
            <a href="/services/electronic-systems/">Electronic Systems</a>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li><a href="/contact/">Contact Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#about">About Us</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="service-content" id="training-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2>Education & Training Services</h2>
      <p>We deliver comprehensive technology training programs designed to upskill your team and keep them at the forefront of innovation. Our expert instructors combine real-world experience with proven teaching methodologies to deliver impactful learning experiences.</p>

      <h3>Software Development Training</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Full-Stack Development</h4><p>Comprehensive training in frontend and backend technologies including React, Node.js, databases, and modern development practices.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Mobile App Development</h4><p>Learn to build native and cross-platform applications using React Native, Flutter, Swift, and Kotlin.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Cloud Development</h4><p>Master cloud platforms including AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud with hands-on projects and certification prep.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>DevOps & CI/CD</h4><p>Learn modern DevOps practices, containerization with Docker, orchestration with Kubernetes, and automation.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Programming Languages</h3>
      <p>Build strong foundations or advance your skills in popular programming languages:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Python:</strong> From basics to advanced topics including data structures, OOP, and frameworks like Django and Flask</li>
        <li><strong>JavaScript/TypeScript:</strong> Modern JavaScript, ES6+, TypeScript, and popular frameworks</li>
        <li><strong>Java:</strong> Core Java, Spring Framework, microservices architecture, and enterprise development</li>
        <li><strong>C# & .NET:</strong> .NET Core, ASP.NET, desktop and web application development</li>
        <li><strong>Go:</strong> Modern concurrent programming, microservices, and cloud-native applications</li>
        <li><strong>Rust:</strong> Systems programming with memory safety and high performance</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Data Science & AI Training</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Machine Learning</h4><p>Comprehensive ML training covering algorithms, model building, and deployment using scikit-learn, TensorFlow.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Deep Learning</h4><p>Neural networks, CNNs, RNNs, and transformer models with practical applications in CV and NLP.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Data Analytics</h4><p>Learn data processing, visualization, and statistical analysis using Python, R, and modern tools.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Big Data Technologies</h4><p>Master Hadoop, Spark, Kafka, and other big data tools for processing large-scale datasets.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Cybersecurity Training</h3>
      <p>Equip your team to defend against modern cyber threats with comprehensive security training:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Ethical Hacking:</strong> Penetration testing techniques, vulnerability assessment, and security auditing</li>
        <li><strong>Network Security:</strong> Firewall configuration, intrusion detection, VPN setup, and network hardening</li>
        <li><strong>Application Security:</strong> Secure coding practices, OWASP Top 10, and security testing methodologies</li>
        <li><strong>Cloud Security:</strong> Securing cloud infrastructure, IAM, compliance, and best practices</li>
        <li><strong>Security Certifications:</strong> Preparation for CEH, CISSP, CompTIA Security+, and more</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Web Technologies</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Frontend Frameworks</h4><p>Master React, Angular, Vue.js, and modern frontend development with responsive design principles.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Backend Development</h4><p>Learn Node.js, Express, Django, Spring Boot, and RESTful API development.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Database Management</h4><p>SQL and NoSQL databases including PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis, and database optimization.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>UI/UX Design</h4><p>Design thinking, wireframing, prototyping, and modern design tools like Figma and Adobe XD.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Corporate Training Programs</h3>
      <p>Customized training solutions tailored to your organization's specific needs:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Team Upskilling:</strong> Identify skill gaps and deliver targeted training to elevate team capabilities</li>
        <li><strong>Technology Transition:</strong> Train teams on new technologies during platform or framework migrations</li>
        <li><strong>Onboarding Programs:</strong> Accelerate new hire productivity with structured learning paths</li>
        <li><strong>Leadership Development:</strong> Technical leadership, architecture, and management training for senior roles</li>
        <li><strong>Certification Bootcamps:</strong> Intensive preparation for professional certifications and exams</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Training Formats</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Instructor-Led Training</h4><p>Live, interactive sessions with expert instructors, hands-on labs, and real-time Q&A support.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Online Courses</h4><p>Self-paced learning with video lessons, coding exercises, and lifetime access to course materials.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Workshops & Bootcamps</h4><p>Intensive short-duration programs focused on specific technologies or skills with project-based learning.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Custom Corporate Training</h4><p>On-site or remote training programs tailored specifically to your team's needs and schedule.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container"><div class="contact-content">
      <h2>Let's Build Something Great Together</h2>
      <p>Ready to transform your business with cutting-edge technology solutions? Get in touch with our team today.</p>
      <div class="contact-info">
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><a href="/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br>Get in touch</a></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span></div>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </section>

</Layout>
